### Upload a file
POST http://localhost:8080/api/files/upload
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="test.txt"
Content-Type: text/plain

Hello from team4you!
--boundary--

### Download a file
GET http://localhost:8080/api/files/download/test.txt

### Delete a file
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/files/delete/test.txt